      }
    },
    {
      "id": "C-II-EX-2",
      "raw": "FOR SALE:  Spring coats.  All fine Scotch serge, for ensembles.  Stoat trimmed, fashioned right.  Black shirred lining, striped.  Effective for brides.  Act quickly. - Abraham Batz, 522 Broad, Telephone Exchange 7104-R.",
      "cipher_system": "concealment",
      "charset": "[\\s\\S]",
      "casesensitive": true,
      "origin": {"originator": "B. NATURAL"},
      "solution": {
        "plaintext": "Police on trail ...",
        "key": "Read 2nd letters of words"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "C-II-EX-3",
      "raw": "How about releasing Tony, the gang chief?  He don't lie, and is not the true slayer either.  Let us be friends.  I am all  right.  Ed Lehr.",
      "charset": "[\\s\\S]",
      "casesensitive": true,
      "cipher_system": "concealment",
      "origin": {"originator": "TITOGI"},
      "solution": {
        "plaintext": "Being held ...",
        "key": "Read every 5th letter"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "C-II-EX-4",
      "raw": "To those friends considering, it is always news, but all filled ciphers disturb happiness with varied answers!",
      "charset": "[\\s\\S]",
      "casesensitive": true,
      "cipher_system": "concealment",
      "origin": {"originator": "TRYIT"},
      "solution": {
